 {"id":"jeffreysprompts.com-6xs","title":"Configure Vercel deployment (vercel.json)","description":"**Details:**
- vercel.json in repository root
- Configure build settings for monorepo
- Set output directory for Next.js app
- Configure rewrites/redirects if needed
- Environment variables setup

**vercel.json:**
```json
{
  "buildCommand": "cd apps/web && bun run build",
  "outputDirectory": "apps/web/.next",
  "installCommand": "bun install",
  "framework": "nextjs",
  "rewrites": [
    { "source": "/registry.json", "destination": "/api/registry" }
  ]
}
```

**Environment Variables:**
- NEXT_PUBLIC_GIT_SHA (set automatically by Vercel)
- JFP_REGISTRY_VERSION (build-time)
- NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL

**Custom Domain:** jeffreysprompts.com

**Reasoning:** Vercel deployment config ensures correct monorepo handling. Environment variables enable version tracking and analytics.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-10T00:33:26.020138672-05:00","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-10T02:06:11.906506203-05:00","closed_at":"2026-01-10T02:06:11.906506203-05:00","close_reason":"vercel.json already configured with framework, buildCommand, installCommand, outputDirectory. Site deploys successfully. Per AGENTS.md, Vercel dashboard has root directory set to apps/web.","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"jeffreysprompts.com-6xs","depends_on_id":"jeffreysprompts.com-r9m","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-10T00:38:20.773175581-05:00","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
